            <title>[LU-1653] Analyze Getattr Aggregation </title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1653</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The basic idea here is to send multiple getattr requests in a single RPC, and appears to be related to bug &lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=18526&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;18526&lt;/a&gt;, although we want do this for both MDT and OST getattr requests.  For now we&apos;re just looking for an analysis of the problem and perhaps a proposed high-level design. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
